@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 13
title 图19  订单状态流转图

[*] --> PENDING_PAYMENT : 创建订单
PENDING_PAYMENT --> PAID : 模拟支付成功
PENDING_PAYMENT --> CANCELLED : 用户主动取消
PENDING_PAYMENT --> EXPIRED : 倒计时超时
PAID --> REFUNDED : 申请退款审核通过\n(后续扩展)

note right of PENDING_PAYMENT
  关联座位状态 LOCKED
end note

note right of PAID
  关联座位 SOLD
  生成 ticket_item
end note

note right of EXPIRED
  座位自动释放为 AVAILABLE
end note

PAID --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]
EXPIRED --> [*]
REFUNDED --> [*]
@enduml
